==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nickelic
<hw>Nick*el"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or containing, nickel; specifically, designating
compounds in which, as contrasted with the <xex>nickelous</xex>
compounds, the metal has a higher valence; <as>as <ex>nickelic</ex>
oxide</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nickeliferous</ent>⟦br⟧
